EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE:

This repository contains educational materials for the course "Laboratorio de 
Introducción al Procesamiento del Lenguaje Natural y LLMs" taught at IFTS N°24 
during the period March-June 2025.

The materials are designed for educational purposes and include:
- Jupyter notebooks with practical exercises
- Theoretical presentations and documentation
- Datasets for learning and experimentation
- Code examples and implementations

Students and educators are encouraged to use, modify, and distribute these 
materials for educational purposes while maintaining proper attribution.

For commercial use or redistribution outside educational contexts, please 
contact the author.

Contact: Prof. Matias Barreto
Institution: IFTS N°24
Course: Laboratorio de Introducción al NLP y LLMs
Period: Marzo-Junio 2025
